comment: * Interface for current physical channel configuration listener.

methods.name: void onPhysicalChannelConfigChanged(@NonNull List<PhysicalChannelConfig> configs)
methods.comment:
* Callback invoked when the current physical channel configuration has changed
         *
         * The calling app should have carrier privileges
         * (see {@link TelephonyManager#hasCarrierPrivileges}) if it does not have the
         * {@link android.Manifest.permission#READ_PRECISE_PHONE_STATE}.
         *
         * @param configs List of the current {@link PhysicalChannelConfig}s
